;Authored books *''As Fire Burns: Of Ontology, Praxis, and Functional Work'', Geelong, Deakin University PhD Thesis, 2000. *(ed. with Bruno Besana), ''Écrits autour de la pensée d'Alain Badiou'', Paris, Éditions L'Harmattan, 2007. *''Alain Badiou: Live Theory'', London: Continuum, 2008. {{ISBN|978-0-8264-9693-5}}. *''Anatomy of Failure: Philosophy and Political Action'', London, Bloomsbury, 2013.
